On the counter you see a cookbook and a knife. Wow! Just like in the movies! You can see a stove. But there isn't a thing on it.

There is an open plain door leading south. You need an exit without a door? You should try going north. You don't like doors? Why not try going west, that entranceway is not blocked by one.
